  "prompt": "How do you see a deleted comment on instagram?",
  "response": "Once a comment is deleted on Instagram, there's no way to retrieve or see it through the app itself. When a comment is deleted, it's permanently removed from the platform's servers. If you're interested in seeing a deleted comment, you could try one of the following methods:\n\n1. **Notifications**: If you had comment notifications enabled for the post, you might still have a notification that shows part of the comment.\n\n2. **Screenshots**: If someone had taken a screenshot of the comment before it was deleted, you might be able to see it that way. \n\n3. **Contact the Commenter**: If you remember who made the comment, you can reach out to them and ask if they remember what they posted.\n\nRemember to respect privacy and consider the reason why the comment might have been deleted in the first place.",
